# Cloudflare response headers (applied by Workers static assets, same as Pages).
# HSTS uses a conservative 6-month max-age with no includeSubDomains/preload so
# it stays reversible. The CSP here only restricts framing; it does not limit
# scripts/styles, so the React Scorecard island and inline scripts keep working.
/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=15552000
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'none'
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
